org.polarsys.chess.chessmlprofile.Dependability.DependableComponent

Interface ErrorModelBehavior

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ErrorModelBehaviorImpl

    public interface ErrorModelBehavior
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Error Model Behavior'. This stereotype is used to attach a user defined error model to an architectural element. It replaces the DependableComponent. See also FLABehavior and SimpleStochasticBehavior.

    The following features are supported:

    • Error Model
    • Base Class
    • Base Instance Specification
    • Base Property
    • Base Connector
    See Also:
    DependableComponentPackage.getErrorModelBehavior()
